<h5 id="subject_598274">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=64562.msg598274#msg598274" rel="nofollow">Re: 龙腾世纪第二章原文Character Creation</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_598274'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_598274'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #3 于:</strong> 2013-12-27, 周五 15:01:28 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_598274_quick_mod"></div>
