<h5 id="subject_598276">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=64562.msg598276#msg598276" rel="nofollow">Re: 龙腾世纪第二章原文Character Creation</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_598276'));undefined;">繁</a>
